1
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,320
Si Qi

2
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:42,600
You're grown up now, time to get married.

3
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,320
Dad, it's your birthday today.

4
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,320
Why are you saying that?

5
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,679
Come on, Dad. Let's buy a strawberry cake.

6
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:47,840
It's a limited edition.

7
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,880
Sheng Yuanzhou.

8
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,840
Isn't this my future father-in-law?

9
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,880
What's going on between you two?

10
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,240
Just guys being guys.

11
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,640
Let it go unsaid.

12
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,599
Sheng Yuanzhou, you...

13
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:10,079
You and Si Qi have an engagement!

14
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,519
How can you...

15
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:12,560
mess around with some outsider?

16
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,000
And...

17
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,200
I know.

18
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,359
Dad, Dad!

19
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:18,400
Sheng Yuanzhou, it's my dad's birthday today.

20
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,760
Can you tone it down a bit?

21
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,799
We're not even married yet.

22
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,920
He's not my father-in-law yet, either.

23
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,959
What, you want me to wish him a happy birthday?

24
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,560
If I don't have some fun while I still can,

25
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,640
then after we get married,

26
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:29,680
I won't be able to do it this openly, right?

27
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,640
You're shameless.

28
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,280
A rich Young Master like me...

29
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,120
Do you really want me to...

30
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,799
tie myself to one woman forever?

31
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,519
If you can't even handle that,

32
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,920
you still want to marry into the Sheng family?

33
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:48,879
Sheng Yuanzhou, I'm telling you.

34
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:52,640
I'm not interested in you or the Sheng family.

35
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,760
You called me here on purpose

36
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,840
just to watch you get slapped?

37
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,920
Take care, father-in-law.

38
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,919
Why did you intentionally make them think

39
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,439
that you got a room with another woman?

40
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,319
If you want to end your engagement to Lin Si Qi,

41
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,159
letting her dad see it with his own eyes

42
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,719
what a player I am

43
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,000
isn't that more direct?

44
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,039
Old foxes like them

45
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,439
don't care how messy your private life is.

46
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,599
They only care whether you've got money.

47
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:33,879
Besides,

48
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,479
the Lin Family hospital is still waiting on

49
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,199
Prosperity Group's money to save it.

50
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:40,400
If you really want to break it off with Lin Si Qi,

51
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,159
it's actually pretty simple.

52
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:44,120
Everyone in our circle knows

53
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,680
Lin Si Qi fell for a poor guy.

54
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,120
With you being such a huge cuckold,

55
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,080
isn't that enough to be

56
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,960
a reason for you to end the engagement?

57
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:53,240
Since they love the Sheng family's money,

58
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:56,039
they won't end the engagement easily.

59
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,039
Yeah, true.

60
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:02,360
Who'd drop a golden goose like the Shengs?

61
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,639
If you really

62
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:06,759
want to dump that girl Lin Si Qi,

63
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,240
why don't you consider

64
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:11,479
a marriage alliance with me?

65
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,360
I'm much more mature than Lin Si Qi,

66
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,080
that naive little girl.

67
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,199
I know how the world works.

68
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,520
When I look at a woman,

69
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,840
I don't think with my dick.

70
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:29,840
You look at her brains,

71
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,840
and her money power.

72
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,080
Women you can sleep with are everywhere.

73
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,360
Women who can make money?

74
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,400
Not many.

75
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,479
Prosperity Group's eldest son

76
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:45,199
actually cares if a woman can make money?

77
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:46,199
As you know,

78
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,240
Prosperity Group is still run by my dad.

79
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,960
I don't want to be a figurehead heir.

80
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:53,719
So...

81
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,680
Got any good ways to make money?

82
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,159
Interesting.

83
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,520
You're not like those lousy men.

84
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,800
You think differently.

85
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:08,800
Ever heard of Hades Club?

86
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,159
Hades Club?

87
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,480
I'm not like Zhu Zipeng, that idiot

88
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,800
who only knows how to play with women.

89
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,000
I'm like you.

90
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,040
Money comes first.

91
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,959
So you started Hades Club.

92
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,519
I don't have that kind of pull.

93
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,040
I just provide them

94
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,360
a place to gather.

95
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:29,519
I make introductions and connections,

96
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:31,240
and earn a little for my trouble.

97
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,759
Anyone who can get into Hades Club

98
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:35,360
is a top-tier tycoon in this country.

99
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,519
Any industry, any field.

100
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,839
All across the nation.

101
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:41,040
The only requirement is money.

102
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,120
After all, you must be on the same level

103
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,360
to play together.

104
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:47,920
So,

105
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:51,879
they're all doing business.

106
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,800
You're something else.

107
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,279
When people come to my place,

108
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,839
it's just to have a few drinks,

109
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,560
make some friends,

110
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,199
talk about global economic trends,

111
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,439
and see what opportunities are out there.

112
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,279
Have you heard of the Pareto principle?

113
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,000
Of course.

114
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,560
It's the same in the wealth world.

115
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:12,120
Jewish people make up

116
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,240
0.2 percent of the world's population,

117
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:14,920
yet they hold

118
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,439
80 percent of the world's wealth.

119
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,519
Hades has its own Pareto principle too.

120
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,160
Hades members

121
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,319
are 0.02% of the nation's population.

122
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,879
That 0.02%

123
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,560
is like the Jewish people.

124
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,240
See those two over there?

125
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,439
The one in the black suit jacket

126
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,879
is the founder of Great Qin Capital.

127
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:42,480
The one who just turned and greeted us

128
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:45,279
is Xiao Hang, Shipping Magnate of the East.

129
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,360
They're the real titans of business.

130
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:51,040
Come. I'll introduce you to new friends.

131
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,120
Hello.

132
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,279
Long time no see.

133
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,120
Let me introduce a new friend.

134
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,000
Prosperity Group's Young Master.

135
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,680
Sheng Yuanzhou.

136
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,399
Welcome, welcome, welcome, brother.

137
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,399
Come, come.

138
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:02,959
Hello, hello.

139
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,199
What you were just saying...

140
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,839
about Dongbao Steel's restructuring,

141
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,480
is it true or not?

142
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:43,519
True or not?

143
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,839
We'll know once the market news drops.

144
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,879
Make sure you seize the chance.

145
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,360
Rich people really do make money so easily

146
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,079
Not like...

147
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,680
...me. I lost it all.

148
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,639
It can jump 20 percent in a single day.

149
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,000
What a shame.

150
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,680
I just don't have enough capital.

151
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,839
Mr. Sheng.

152
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:25,839
What do you need such a huge sum for?

153
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,319
You don't need to ask so much.

154
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,839
But...

155
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,279
Chairman Sheng won't allow you...

156
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,680
...to use company funds whenever you want.

157
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,040
In your personal account,

158
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,680
you get 150,000 a month as spending money.

159
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,759
And you spend it all every month.

160
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:36,800
This month,

161
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,959
you paid for Zhang Xiaobei's family's...

162
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,079
...100,000 in medical bills.

163
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,759
Right now, in the account,

164
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,079
there's only 50,000 left.

165
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,040
So I don't have...

166
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,240
...any other personal assets?

167
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,879
Every time you use money,

168
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,079
you need Chairman Sheng's approval.

169
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,480
If I could invest a few million more...

170
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:56,480
Then when I go back to my parents,

171
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,120
they won't have to worry about money.

172
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,519
But where am I supposed to get more money?

173
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,199
Borrow it.

174
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,000
Yeah.

175
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,800
A while back, didn't I make my dad...

176
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,560
...mad?

177
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,959
So he froze my card.

178
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,839
I figured, with news about Dongbao Steel...

179
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:16,759
...this good,

180
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,879
I couldn't just let it go to waste.

181
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:21,240
Prosperity Group's Young Master borrows?

182
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,639
Even if you don't have cash on hand,

183
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,040
you've still got assets.

184
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,000
Assets? What assets?

185
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,720
That land your mom left you.

186
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,440
It's zoned into the Free Trade Zone now.

187
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,679
It must be worth hundreds of millions.

188
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,759
Sell it,

189
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,080
and you'll have money.

190
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,639
Land...

191
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,600
Sheng Yuanzhou's mom left him...

192
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,120
...that huge a piece of land?

193
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,639
If he sells it,

194
00:09:03,639 --> 00:09:04,720
it's easily over a hundred million.

195
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,600
Back then, why did his mom...

196
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,320
...buy such a huge stretch of wasteland?

197
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:24,519
Are you...

198
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,399
Young Master?

199
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,399
It's me.

200
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,840
Granny Shen, who chased you to feed you.

201
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,639
Granny Shen...

202
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:35,480
I'm old, you don't recognize me anymore.

203
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,120
How could I not recognize you?

204
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,519
Look how gloomy it is.

205
00:09:39,519 --> 00:09:40,600
And it's drizzling, too.

206
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,320
I just couldn't see you clearly.

207
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,759
You sneaked out to see your mom again.

208
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,279
Come this way.

209
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,480
Didn't Sheng Yuanzhou's mom pass away?

210
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,919
Take a quick look and hurry back.

211
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,559
If your father finds out, he'll be mad.

212
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,720
I said it before.

213
00:10:19,279 --> 00:10:20,240
Without my permission,

214
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,720
no one is allowed to go there.

215
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:23,320
Sneaking over there...

216
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,320
What were you trying to do?

217
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,360
But...

218
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,720
That's my mom!

219
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,279
Shut up.

220
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,960
You forgot the rules again, didn't you?

221
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,000
In this family, you must not mention her.

222
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,399
Let me tell you.

223
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,600
In this house, you don't get to do...

224
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,240
...whatever you feel like.

225
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,320
Today, you're going to kneel right here.

226
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:40,639
And reflect on it properly.

227
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,200
All I did was visit my mother's grave.

228
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,080
Was that really worth such a huge tantrum?

229
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:55,279
No...

230
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:57,000
Something's off. There's always a reason.

231
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,279
I haven't had Granny Shen's food in ages.

232
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,679
Little Young Master.

233
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,879
Why are you here again?

234
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,399
All these years,

235
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,600
you've been watching this place alone.

236
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,480
I wanted to keep you company.

237
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:24,720
No, no.

238
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,200
Hurry back.

239
00:11:26,759 --> 00:11:28,600
Didn't your dad punish you yesterday?

240
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,200
And you still came after that?

241
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,440
This is my mom's grave.

242
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,960
Why can't I come?

243
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,600
Every time,

244
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:42,000
I see that flower bed up front,

245
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,919
I remember Madam, taking you as a kid...

246
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,200
...to plant flowers.

247
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,440
This place...

248
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,120
It's full of memories of you two.

249
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,320
Madam...

250
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,639
Look at the Young Master.

251
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:01,639
He misses you so much.

252
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:03,840
How could you be so heartless?

253
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,600
You just left him behind and walked away.

254
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,399
Your father won't let you come.

255
00:12:09,799 --> 00:12:11,120
So don't go against him.

256
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,039
If he punishes you,

257
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:15,159
Madam will be upset.

258
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,759
Where Sheng Yuanzhou grew up...

259
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,120
Why won't Sheng Shizhong let him come back?

260
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,159
That's because my dad is unreasonable.

261
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,960
I'm not scared of him.

262
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:27,720
But you can't blame him for all of it.

263
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:30,960
After all, your mom betrayed him first.

264
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:32,600
Betrayed?

265
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:34,279
Sheng Yuanzhou's mother...

266
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:35,879
She cheated.

267
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:38,399
Granny Shen.

268
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,639
What really happened back then?

269
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,440
Those awful things...

270
00:12:46,759 --> 00:12:47,799
Shouldn't be remembered.

271
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,559
Granny Shen, please tell me.

272
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,879
I'm grown up now.

273
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:52,919
I have the right to know.

274
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,320
No one will tell me.

275
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,559
Only you can.

276
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,639
You're the only one who remembers her,

277
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,320
The only one who still talks about her.

278
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,879
Only you can tell me about her.

279
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,200
You don't want, in a few more years,

280
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,080
For me to forget even my mom, do you?

281
00:13:09,879 --> 00:13:10,559
All right.

282
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:12,639
Then I'll tell you about her.

283
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:18,200
Truth is, your parents loved each other.

284
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,000
They were childhood sweethearts after all.

285
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,000
After you were born,

286
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,120
They were even closer than most couples.

287
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,000
But somehow,

288
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,679
Your mom suddenly...

289
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:36,080
Fell for the family driver, Hu Jin.

290
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:38,320
She made a fuss every day to go see him.

291
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,919
Crying and causing scenes.

292
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:42,440
The family couldn't stop her at all.

293
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,159
Madam!

294
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:44,320
Madam!

295
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:45,639
Madam!

296
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,440
Later...

297
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,440
After that driver left,

298
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,759
Your mom took her own life.

299
00:13:53,399 --> 00:13:54,399
So...

300
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:57,039
Sheng Shizhong doesn't want to bring up

301
00:13:57,039 --> 00:13:58,159
being a cuckold.

302
00:13:58,639 --> 00:13:59,720
That's why he won't let anyone set foot in

303
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,159
Sheng Yuanzhou's mother's grave site.

304
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:02,759
Now...

305
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,399
You understand your father's pain, right?

306
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:16,639
Mr. Sheng.

307
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,000
Mr. Sheng.

308
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,879
It's time. You should go.

309
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:22,879
Go where?

310
00:14:23,039 --> 00:14:25,080
Today is your appointment with Dr. Chen.

311
00:14:25,399 --> 00:14:26,240
Dr. Chen...

312
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:31,279
I forgot.

313
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:31,879
Let's go.

314
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,720
How have you been feeling lately?

315
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:37,840
Same as always.

316
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:40,399
Are you still taking your meds on time?

317
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:41,559
Meds...

318
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,879
Do you still keep having that nightmare?

319
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,080
Sheng Yuanzhou...

320
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:50,200
You've got quite a few secrets.

321
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:52,720
Dr. Chen.

322
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:56,279
Do you still remember, when I was little,

323
00:14:56,279 --> 00:14:56,919
The first time you met me,

324
00:14:56,919 --> 00:14:57,879
What I was like?

325
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,159
You were eight then.

326
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,200
Very quiet.

327
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,600
Very sweet.

328
00:15:03,879 --> 00:15:05,039
You loved drawing.

329
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,679
Do you still have my drawings?

330
00:15:08,039 --> 00:15:08,519
Of course.

331
00:15:08,799 --> 00:15:09,360
I want to see them.

332
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,840
Lately I miss those childhood days.

333
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,799
I miss who you were back then, too.

334
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,200
So little.

335
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:22,639
You always sat there quietly,

336
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:25,440
Drawing the world as you saw it.

337
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:27,120
From your pictures,

338
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:29,480
I could tell you had a

339
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:31,279
Warm, gentle heart.

340
00:15:31,919 --> 00:15:35,200
You have eyes to see the world's beauty.
